#. module: headhunter
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:headhunter.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The Opportunity will be qualified and when the need is understood move the "
"Opportunity to Proposition. It will automatically send an email with a "
"Signature Request (Studio : Automated Action). That Signature Request hold "
"an already\n"
"            signed, from Company, Service Agreement with default terms and "
"filled values."
msgstr ""
"Når salgsmuligheden er kvalificeret, og behovet er klarlagt, flyttes den til "
"\"Forslag\". En automatisk e-mail med underskriftsanmodning (Studio: "
"automatiseret handling) sendes, hvor serviceaftalen\n"
"            fra virksomheden med standardbetingelser og udfyldte værdier "
"allerede er inkluderet."

#. module: headhunter
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:headhunter.welcome_article_body
msgid "The business is based on two flows :"
msgstr "Virksomheden har to grundlæggende flows:"

#. module: headhunter
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:headhunter.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"This customized form will create an opportunity in the CRM, with the right "
"information and in option, the jobs they're interested in."
msgstr ""
"Formularen opretter en salgsmulighed i CRM, der indeholder de nødvendige "
"oplysninger samt de stillinger, brugeren har markeret som interessante."

#. module: headhunter
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:headhunter.welcome_article_body
msgid "This form will create an applicant in the Recruitment app."
msgstr "Formularen opretter automatisk en ansøger i Rekrutteringsappen."

#. module: headhunter
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:headhunter.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"This setup is for Talent Acquisition Agency / Recruitment Agency / Staffing "
"Agency. Those agencies work on two levels and with two different audiences. "
"The customers will comes through their website, contact them and will be "
"managed\n"
"            under market opportunities. The consultants or freelances will "
"apply through the career pages and be managed by the company to match with "
"the market opportunities."
msgstr ""
"Konfigurationen er målrettet personale- og rekrutteringsbureauer, som "
"opererer på to niveauer med hver sin målgruppe. Kunderne kommer via "
"hjemmesiden, tages i behandling og administreres\n"
"            under markedsmulighederne. Konsulenter og freelancere ansøger "
"via karrieresiderne og matches af virksomheden med de relevante "
"markedsmuligheder."

#. module: headhunter
#: model_terms:hr.job,website_description:headhunter.hr_job_6
#: model_terms:hr.job,website_description:headhunter.hr_job_7
msgid "Trainings"
msgstr "Uddannelser"

#. module: headhunter
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:headhunter.homepage
msgid ""
"Trust us&amp;nbsp;to be your strategic partner in talent acquisition. "
"Elevate your organization with exceptional professionals today!<br/>"
msgstr ""
"Stol på os&amp;nbsp;som din strategiske partner inden for talentanskaffelse. "
"Styrk din organisation med ekstraordinære fagfolk!<br/>"

#. module: headhunter
#: model_terms:hr.job,website_description:headhunter.hr_job_7
msgid "Valid work permit for Belgium"
msgstr "Gyldig arbejdstilladelse til Belgien"

#. module: headhunter
#: model_terms:hr.job,website_description:headhunter.hr_job_10
msgid ""
"We are currently accepting spontaneous applications from skilled "
"professionals in various fields. Our agency specializes in finding top-notch "
"candidates for our clients across multiple industries, including (but not\n"
"                                                limited to):"
msgstr ""
"Vi modtager løbende uopfordrede ansøgninger fra kvalificerede fagfolk inden "
"for forskellige områder. Vores bureau er specialiseret i at finde "
"førsteklasses kandidater til vores kunder fra forskellige brancher, herunder "
"(men ikke\n"
"                                                begrænset til):"

#. module: headhunter
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:headhunter.services
msgid "We are in good company."
msgstr "Vi er i godt selskab."

#. module: headhunter
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:headhunter.services
msgid ""
"We have a history of successfully placing candidates in key positions across "
"various industries.&amp;nbsp;"
msgstr ""
"Vi har med dokumenteret succes formidlet kandidater til centrale stillinger "
"i en række forskellige brancher.&amp;nbsp;"

#. module: headhunter
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:headhunter.services
msgid ""
"We help you acquire new talents from the market, based on your needs and "
"specifications.&amp;nbsp;"
msgstr ""
"Vi hjælper dig med at finde nye talenter på markedet, baseret på dine behov "
"og krav.&amp;nbsp;"

#. module: headhunter
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:headhunter.services
msgid ""
"We prioritize discretion in all our dealings, providing a secure and "
"confidential recruitment process.&amp;nbsp;"
msgstr ""
"Vi lægger stor vægt på diskretion i alle vores forretninger og sikrer en "
"tryg og fortrolig ansættelsesproces.&amp;nbsp;"

#. module: headhunter
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:headhunter.services
msgid ""
"We understand that every organization is unique, so we tailor our search "
"strategy to meet your specific needs.&amp;nbsp;"
msgstr ""
"Hver virksomhed er unik, og derfor skræddersyr vi vores søgestrategi, så den "
"matcher dine specifikke behov.&amp;nbsp;"

