msgstr "Hvad er godt ved jobbet?"

#. module: headhunter
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:headhunter.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"When Opportunities will open, and the applicant is matching requirements, "
"you can link the Opportunity/ies to his Applicant record with a Many-to-Many "
"object linked to the CRM (Studio : Customization of the Applicant view)."
msgstr ""
"Hvis der opstår en salgsmulighed, og ansøgeren opfylder kravene, kan du "
"knytte salgsmuligheden/salgsmulighederne til ansøgerens data via et mange-"
"til-mange-objekt i CRM (Studio: Tilpasning af ansøgervisningen)."

#. module: headhunter
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:headhunter.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"When Service Agreement is signed, the opportunity is manually moved to "
"\"Agreement Signed\", the Sales can open a discussion with the Recruitment "
"team, and Opportunity will go, and stay, in Recruitment stage, for a while."
msgstr ""
"Når serviceaftalen er underskrevet, overføres muligheden manuelt til status "
"\"Aftale underskrevet\". Salgsteamet kan koordinere med rekrutteringsteamet, "
"mens muligheden midlertidigt forbliver i rekrutteringsfasen."

#. module: headhunter
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:headhunter.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"When the applicant is created, an activity for a call will be automatically "
"created and assigned to the Recruiter (Studio : Automated Action). The "
"applicant will get a confirmation email from Recruitment Stage configuration."
msgstr ""
"Ved oprettelse af en ansøger oprettes automatisk en opkaldsaktivitet, der "
"tildeles rekrutteringskonsulenten (Studio: automatiseret handling). "
"Ansøgeren modtager samtidig en bekræftelsesmail baseret på "
"rekrutteringsfasens indstillinger."

#. module: headhunter
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:headhunter.services
msgid ""
"With an extensive international network, we can source talent from around "
"the world"
msgstr ""
"Takket være vores brede internationale netværk kan vi identificere og "
"tiltrække talenter globalt"

#. module: headhunter
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:headhunter.services
msgid ""
"With our experience, we'll help you analyse your company and the vacancies "
"that you should propose, or the market and the vibes in the Recruitment "
"area.&amp;nbsp;"
msgstr ""
"Vi bruger vores erfaring til at analysere din virksomhed, vurdere relevante "
"stillinger og kortlægge markedet samt rekrutteringstendenser.&amp;nbsp;"

